<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.10">
<l>aṉṟu pāratat taivar tūtaṉāy</l>
<l>ceṉṟa māyaṉaic ceṅkaṇ māliṉai</l>
<l>maṉṟi lārppukaḻ maṅkai vāḷkali</l>
<l>kaṉṟi colvallārk kalla lillaiyē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>For those who master the words of sword[- bearing] Kalikaṉṟi</l>
<l>Of Maṅkai whose praise is spread in assemblies,</l>
<l>About bright-eyed Māl, Māyaṉ who once arrived as a messenger</l>
<l>Of the Five in the Bhārata [War], there will be no sorrows.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
